    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Goblin runners are the skirmishing vanguard of the Svellheim goblin clans — fast, nimble, and cowardly in exactly the right measure. They dart in to club a distracted hero and dart right back out before the return swing comes. Their Crafty feature lets them exploit every sightline and alley, and they excel at leading enemies into traps or out of formations. In numbers they become genuinely dangerous.</p>",
